OL,6,FA council in the South East of England
OL,7,Fhas warned it will have to make
OL,8,Fextensive cuts to services due to
OL,9,Fincreasing levels of homelessness.
OL,11,FEastbourne Borough Council is facing
OL,12,F'colossal financial pressure' created
OL,13,Fby increasing levels of homelessness
OL,14,Fand temporary accommodation placements.
OL,16,FThe authority has already made savings
OL,17,Fof more than #3 million from the 2024/
OL,18,F2025 budget and plans to make a
OL,19,Ffurther saving #2.5m of savings, but
OL,20,Fsays is at risk of being unable to set
OL,21,Fa balanced budget.
