OL,3,CCouncil facing 'colossal financial
OL,4,Cpressure' due to levels of homelessness
OL,6,F"Over the last 12 months I have
OL,7,Frepeatedly warned that the increasing
OL,8,Fcosts we are shouldering are wholly
OL,9,Funsustainable. I took our concerns to
OL,10,FWestminster and with a cross-party
OL,11,Fgroup of over 50 council leaders,
OL,12,Finvited ministers and MPs to engage
OL,13,Fwith us.
OL,15,F"While we remain unwavering in our
OL,16,Fmoral and statutory commitment to
OL,17,Fprovide accommodation for those in
OL,18,Fneed, we continue our campaign and
OL,19,Fappeal to the new government for
OL,20,Furgent solutions.
