OL,6,FThe latest figures, to December 31
OL,7,Flast year, showed a new record high of
OL,8,F145,800 children in temporary
OL,9,Faccommodation, up by a fifth on 20
OL,10,Fyears ago when records for this
OL,11,Fmeasure began.
OL,13,FThere were a total of 112,660
OL,14,Fhouseholds in temporary accommodation
OL,15,Fin England, of which 71,280 were
OL,16,Fhouseholds with children, by the end
OL,17,Fof last year.
