OL,6,FA Ministry of Housing, Communities &
OL,7,FLocal Government spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Homelessness levels have sky-rocketed
OL,9,Fand too many families are living in
OL,10,Ftemporary accommodation in our towns
OL,11,Fand cities, including in Eastbourne.
OL,13,F"We will take the action needed to
OL,14,Ftackle this issue and develop a long-
OL,15,Fterm, cross-government strategy
OL,16,Fworking with Mayors and Councils to
OL,17,Fput Britain back on track to ending
OL,18,Fhomelessness."
